title: F1 API Documentation
p1: Welcome to the Formula 1 API! This API provides access to a wealth of data related to Formula 1 races, drivers, teams, circuits, and more.
p2: All the data its provided in JSON format and its ready to use. Simply fetch https://f1api.dev with the endpoint that you like.
table-caption: A list of all the API endpoints.
blog-entrance: In this blog we will be going through each update of the API. As well as news and curiosities related to F1.
blog-advertise: Note that the changelog is written in English, but news about F1 is written in Spanish.
